'''苏豪广场'''（Soho Square）是[[伦敦苏豪区|伦敦苏豪区]]的一个广场，[[牛津街|牛津街]]以南，[[查令十字|查令十字路]]以西。广场周边的街道，从北按顺时针方向，分别为苏豪街（Soho Street）、 萨顿行（Sutton Row）、[[希腊街|希腊街]]、贝特曼斯大楼（Batemans Buildings）、弗里思街（Frith Street）和卡莱尔街（Carlisle Street）。在花园的中心，有一个独特的半木园丁小屋。在夏季，举行露天免费音乐会。

苏豪广场开辟于1670年代。它原名国王广场（King Square），得名于[[查理二世|查理二世]]，其雕像立于广场中心。到19世纪初，这座雕像的情形已经相当悲惨<ref name=Cibber>[http://www.british-history.ac.uk/report.aspx?compid=41027&strquery=Cibber "Soho Square Area: Portland Estate: Soho Square Garden"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.british-history.ac.uk/report.aspx?compid=41027&strquery=Cibber |date=20141019163825 }} in ''Survey of London'' volumes 33 and 34 (1966) [[St_Anne_Soho|St Anne Soho]], pp. 51-53. Date accessed: 12 January 2008.</ref>，1875年被移走保管，1938年恢复<ref>[http://www.londonremembers.com/memorial/?id=216 Photo of the statue] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061030210744/http://www.londonremembers.com/memorial/?id=216 |date=2006-10-30 }}</ref>。

从1778年到1801年，苏豪广场21号设有著名的白宫妓院（White House brothel）。<ref>{{cite book | last = During | first = Simon | authorlink =  | coauthors =  | title = Modern Enchantments: The Cultural Power of Secular Magic | publisher = Harvard University Press | date = 2004 | location =  | pages = 110–111 | url = http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=2eEK-55hgKMC&pg=PA110&lpg=PA110&dq=%22the+white+house%22+%22soho+square%22&source=web&ots=JkH9BhyibY&sig=PpT98BwCaKDDi9ymW6QYHBujcMk&hl=en&sa=X&oi=book_result&resnum=2&ct=result#PPA110,M1 | doi =  | id = ''"... the famous magic brothel, the White House at Soho Square, in which commercial sex was enhanced by dark, baroque special-effects and natural magic devices"'' | isbn = 9780674013711 | access-date = 2011-04-28 | archive-date = 2020-06-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200614070402/https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=2eEK-55hgKMC&pg=PA110&lpg=PA110&dq=%22the+white+house%22+%22soho+square%22&source=web&ots=JkH9BhyibY&sig=PpT98BwCaKDDi9ymW6QYHBujcMk&hl=en&sa=X&oi=book_result&resnum=2&ct=result#PPA110,M1 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

苏豪广场8号和9号是[[伦敦法国新教教堂|伦敦法国新教教堂]]，建于1891-93年。广场上还有大型天主教堂[[圣巴特利爵教堂_(苏豪广场)|圣巴特利爵教堂]]。

苏豪广场拥有数家媒体机构，包括英国电影分级委员会，[[20世纪福克斯|20世纪福克斯]]，[[保罗·麦卡特尼|保罗·麦卡特尼]]的MPL Communications等。

